WEBVTT

00:02.041 --> 00:04.208
-Okay, let's take up the
homework from last night,
please.

00:04.250 --> 00:06.500
Yes, Lori?

00:06.542 --> 00:09.500
-Sir, I know you didn't assign
question number four, but what
is moral relativism?

00:09.542 --> 00:12.166
-Lori, I didn't assign it
because...

00:12.208 --> 00:14.166
