Nice hooker boots.

05:19.375 --> 05:21.959
-Good Tim, how are you?
-What?

05:23.667 --> 05:27.041
-Did you hear what he said?
-Well I am so glad that I could
help you out Gerry.

05:29.417 --> 05:31.959
-He's got a point, you know.
-Okay, I'll see you at lunch.

05:32.000 --> 05:34.750
[Lisa]: Drop by anytime.

05:34.792 --> 05:36.959
[Knock on door]

05:38.500 --> 05:40.417
-[Simon]: Hey Bill!
Can I come in?

05:40.458 --> 05:43.417
-Ah, shouldn't you be at school?
-Yeah, I took a personal day.

05:43.458 --> 05:45.959
