-Nice to meet you.

07:02.750 --> 07:04.875
[With accent]: Scottish right?

07:04.917 --> 07:09.500
Only my favourite accent to do,
and I've been working
pretty hard at it.

07:09.542 --> 07:12.500
Won't you indulge me
for a moment?
-What? What'd you say?

07:12.542 --> 07:16.000
-Gerry, close your eyes
and see if you can tell
who's speaking right now.

07:16.041 --> 07:18.583
