-Och aye, calm down ya wee
bugger.

07:18.625 --> 07:21.709
I'm just talking to your dad...
-Is this guy kidding me on.

07:21.750 --> 07:24.834
-Nope.
No, no, I would never kid.

07:24.875 --> 07:28.250
I'm just relishing the chance
to practice my accent.

07:29.667 --> 07:31.834
-Okay.
-What brings you by the school?

07:31.875 --> 07:34.250
-I just came by to pay a
wee visit with my son.

07:34.291 --> 07:36.959
