you say Gerry? Bring him to
your class. It'll be fun.

07:55.375 --> 07:57.583
-Yeah, yeah I guess.

07:57.625 --> 07:59.709
-Och, aye great,
then it's all settled then.

07:59.750 --> 08:02.875
