you all to my father.

08:17.000 --> 08:20.583
-Hello kids.
-[Gerry laughs]: Hello.

08:20.625 --> 08:23.375
My dad was a teacher
in his day.

08:23.417 --> 08:27.458
So this is really exciting
and cool for me to have
him watching me teach.

08:27.500 --> 08:31.458
